comments: Young (ATL) establishes himself in Irving's (BKN) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.

A 24 second violation is correctly whistled against the Hawks.
Harris (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Huerter's (ATL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.

Collins (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in Harris' (BKN) path and absorbs the contact.

Young (ATL) and Harris (BKN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Reddish (ATL) legally contest Harden's (BKN) jump shot attempt.

Reddish (ATL) is moving alongside Durant's (BKN) path and marginal contact occurs during his dunk attempt.
Harris (BKN) is moving alongside Young's (ATL) path when marginal body contact occurs, which does not affect Young's SQBR.
Irving (BKN) briefly places his hand on Huerter's (ATL) side and quickly removes it while contesting Huerter's shot attempt at the basket.

comments: Durant (BKN) is the last person to touch the ball before going out of bounds.
